OL,4,G0205FTrucking Hell
OL,5,     GIn Warwickshire Dave Crouch comes
OL,6,     Gto the rescue a tipper truck gets
OL,7,     Gstuck in deep mud on an isolated
OL,8,     Gfarm track. And a 26-ton truck
OL,9,     Gbreaks down beside the London Eye.
OL,10,G0305FTrucking Hell
OL,11,     GA bin lorry has come off a
OL,12,     Gcountry lane, its wheels slipping
OL,13,     Gin mud, and a box van trailer
OL,14,     Gwith has been uncoupled and left
OL,15,     Gwith the front supported solely
OL,16,     Gby its Landing Legs.
